snippet.title: Ultracore (formerly Project Hardcore) - Name Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
After nearly 25 years of deep sleep, Hardcore will finally be published with the new name Ultracore this year.
Developed by one of the biggest video game developer studios on the planet, Ultracore is a part of video game history and we feel honored to release this game in Spring 2019.
